Q.1 Write messaging beans which accepts operation_code tablename,
cloumnnames and values in a string . The pean parses the string and
perform the operation on table. The message format is following

<operation>:,<table_name>:<columnname1,
columnname2...><value1,value2..)<where clause>

eg.
“I:emp: ename,sal,phone:’prakash’,3400,234567’:’’

or
“U:emp: sal:3400:where empid=5”

or
“D:emp: :where empid=5”

I,U,D stands for Insert update and delete respectively.








